---
import { SITE } from '~/config.mjs';
import { getCanonical, getHomePermalink } from '~/utils/permalinks';
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const meta = {
	title: SITE.title,
	description: SITE.description,
	canonical: getCanonical(getHomePermalink()),
};
---

<Layout {meta}>
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
			<div class="py-12 md:py-20">
				<div class="text-center pb-4 md:pb-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
					<h1
						class="text-5xl md:text-[3.50rem] font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading text-red-500"
					>
						Privacy Policy
					</h1>
					<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
							Privacy is important to us. It is our policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may
							collect from you across our website, <a
								href="https://www.mostlywhat.systems"
								class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300"
								>www.mostlywhat.systems</a
							>, and other sites we own and operate.
						</p>
						<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">Last Updated 15th November 2022</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="pb-4 md:pb-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
				<!-- Privacy Policy -->
				<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
					<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading text-red-500">
						Introduction
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						This privacy notice for MostlyWhat Systems ("Company," "we," "us," or "our"), describes how and why we might
						collect, store, use, and/or share ("process") your information when you use our services ("Services"), such
						as when you:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<li>
							- Visit our website at www.mostlywhat.systems, or any website of ours that links to this privacy notice.
						</li>
						<li>- Engage with us in other related ways, including any sales, marketing, or events</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						Questions or concerns? Reading this privacy notice will help you understand your privacy rights and choices.
						If you do not agree with our policies and practices, please do not use our Services. If you still have any
						questions or concerns, please contact us at admin@mostlywhat.systems.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
					<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading text-red-500">
						Summary
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold">
						This summary provides key points from our privacy notice, but you can find out more details about any of
						these topics by clicking the link following each key point or by using our table of contents below to find
						the section you are looking for. You can also click <a
							href="#toc"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to go directly to our table of contents.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<b class="font-bold">What personal information do we process?</b> When you visit, use, or navigate our Services,
						we may process personal information depending on how you interact with MostlyWhat Systems and the Services, the
						choices you make, and the products and features you use. Click <a
							href="#personalinfo"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to learn more.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<span class="font-bold">Do we process any sensitive personal information?</span> We do not process sensitive
						personal information.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<span class="font-bold">Do we receive any information from third parties?</span> We do not receive any information
						from third parties.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<b class="font-bold">How do we process your information?</b> We process your information to provide, improve,
						and administer our Services, communicate with you, for security and fraud prevention, and to comply with law.
						We may also process your information for other purposes with your consent. We process your information only when
						we have a valid legal reason to do so. Click <a
							href="#infouse"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to learn more.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<b class="font-bold">In what situations and with which parties do we share personal information?</b> We may share
						information in specific situations and with specific third parties. Click <a
							href="#whoshare"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to learn more.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<b class="font-bold">How do we keep your information safe?</b> We have organizational and technical processes
						and procedures in place to protect your personal information. However, no electronic transmission over the internet
						or information storage technology can be guaranteed to be 100% secure, so we cannot promise or guarantee that
						hackers, cybercriminals, or other unauthorized third parties will not be able to defeat our security and improperly
						collect, access, steal, or modify your information. Click <a
							href="#infosafe"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to learn more.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<b class="font-bold">What are your rights?</b> Depending on where you are located geographically, the applicable
						privacy law may mean you have certain rights regarding your personal information. Click <a
							href="#privacyrights"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to learn more.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<b class="font-bold">How long do we keep your information?</b> We keep your information for as long as necessary
						to fulfill the purposes for which we collect it, including for the purposes of satisfying any legal, accounting,
						or reporting requirements. Click <a
							href="#infostore"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to learn more.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						<b class="font-bold">How do you exercise your rights?</b>The easiest way to exercise your rights is by
						contacting us. We will consider and act upon any request in accordance with applicable data protection laws.
					</p>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400">
						Want to learn more about what MostlyWhat Systems does with any information we collect? Click <a
							href="#toc"
							class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300">here</a
						> to review the notice in full.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="toc" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
			<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading text-red-500">
				Table of Contents
			</h2>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
				<li class="mb-2">
					<a href="#infocollect" class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300"
						>1. What information do we collect?</a
					>
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					<a href="#infouse" class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300"
						>2. How do we process your information?</a
					>
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					<a href="#legalbases" class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300"
						>3. What legal bases do we rely on to process your personal information?</a
					>
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					<a href="#infosafe" class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300"
						>How do we keep your information safe?</a
					>
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					<a href="#privacyrights" class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300"
						>What are your rights?</a
					>
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					<a href="#infostore" class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:text-red-300"
						>How long do we keep your information?</a
					>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
